Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}东南亚的遥远角落里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}坐落着珊瑚礁三角区{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里的珊瑚礁种类之繁多 堪称首屈一指{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:01:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}海底城市里挤满了各种各样的生物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.84,0:01:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}与拥挤的大都市一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.72,0:01:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}各种生物都要争夺生存空间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}还有伴侣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是珊瑚礁也是一个充满了机遇的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.88,0:01:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}墨鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.56,0:02:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}猎捕螃蟹是它的专长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.08,0:02:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是大螃蟹却是极其危险的猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.36,0:02:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的爪子强劲有力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.32,0:02:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}然而墨鱼 却有着非凡的天赋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.60,0:02:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的皮肤中含有数百万个色素细胞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.16,0:02:46.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}凭借这些细胞 墨鱼能够变化出色彩各异的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}万千形态{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:03:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这一招显然把螃蟹迷惑住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}尽管墨鱼很聪明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但要论体积 还是鲨鱼更大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.04,0:03:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}另外鲨鱼也会以墨鱼为食{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}是时候消失了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}墨鱼重回猎场{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.04,0:04:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它发现了新的目标 但还是使用了相同的催眠术{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.96,0:04:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}动物如果能在这繁忙的海底城市里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:22.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}立足的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.08,0:04:25.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}就会获得丰厚的奖赏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.67,0:04:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚礁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.76,0:04:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚在热带地区温暖清澈的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}浅水域为自己建造石灰岩家园{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些珊瑚礁所占的海底面积{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.16,0:05:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}连千分之一都不到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.96,0:05:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}然而这里却是世界上四分之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.52,0:05:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}已知海洋生物的家园{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.40,0:05:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些珊瑚礁的结构复杂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.28,0:05:19.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}变化极为丰富{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们为许许多多的居民提供各种各样的家园{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.16,0:05:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}从阁楼套房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}到偏僻巢穴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在澳大利亚的大堡礁上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}一条鳃棘鲈靠猎捕小鱼为生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.16,0:05:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是如果你连缝隙都穿不过的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.12,0:05:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}你要如何在这里找到食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.68,0:06:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}而且鳃棘鲈还有一个对手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.32,0:06:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这个绝顶聪明的对手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.28,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}寻找的也是同一种猎物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.32,0:06:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这个对手就是章鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.68,0:06:51.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它能穿过非常狭小的缝隙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:01.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}就算是这样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.68,0:07:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它的猎物也常常逃走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.28,0:07:17.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}如果它们合作呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.48,0:07:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}鳃棘鲈身上的颜色变浅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}试图吸引章鱼的注意力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.52,0:07:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它还表演了倒立{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.08,0:08:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}鳃棘鲈不仅是在给章鱼发出信号{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它还指出了猎物的藏身之所{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}章鱼到达了里面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.56,0:08:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这条鱼慌张起来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}直直地朝着鳃棘鲈的嘴里游去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.56,0:08:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}得到奖励的有时候是章鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.60,0:08:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}有时候则是鳃棘鲈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这两种不同的动物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}发现团队合作能让它们在珊瑚礁城市里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}大获成功{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.36,0:09:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}事实上 团队合作精神正是珊瑚礁世界的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.04,0:09:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}生存基础{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚本身也要依赖合作关系{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}只不过它们的合作要亲密得多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚是一种类海葵动物的集群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}也就是珊瑚虫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.00,0:09:54.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些不过只有沙粒那么大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.72,0:10:00.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在每个珊瑚虫组织里生活的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.92,0:10:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}是我们的肉眼无法识别的 类植物微小细胞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.28,0:10:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在白天充足的热带阳光下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些类植物细胞蓬勃生长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.20,0:10:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}可为珊瑚虫提供90％以上的食物{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}天黑时 珊瑚虫用自己的触手{\r}
