Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.88,0:10:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚虫还会从海水中提取碳酸钙{\r}
