Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.72,0:11:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚集群能够持续生长数百年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}有些或许能达到千年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们的建造物甚至能达到一所房子那么大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.80,0:11:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们建造的最大的城市 当属大堡礁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.64,0:11:40.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}大堡礁纵贯于澳大利亚东北海岸 全长两千三百公里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}不论珊瑚礁位于何处 里头总是一派活跃的景象{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}黎明时分 日班开始了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:06.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}与之相伴的是一首{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.72,0:12:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}由鱼虾和珊瑚礁其他住户一同合唱的海底乐曲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.04,0:12:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这个城市的每个居民都有自己的角色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.04,0:12:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}食腐动物 例如海参{\r}
