Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.08,0:12:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}鹦哥鱼咬下大块的珊瑚{\r}
