Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:57.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}再将无法消化的珊瑚排泄出来形成沙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.24,0:13:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在婆罗洲这里 绿海龟{\r}
