Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这只母龟起得很早 它比其他绿海龟提前一步出发了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.48,0:13:53.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}为了到达那里 绿海龟要沿着珊瑚礁游很长一段距离{\r}
