Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.20,0:14:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}龟岩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.24,0:14:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}一代又一代的海龟来到这里 岩上方已经被磨出了一个凹陷处{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.12,0:14:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这里是鲇鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.88,0:14:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}和刺尾鱼的家园{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.96,0:14:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们为访客清洗身体 将访客身上的海藻寄生虫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.04,0:14:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}以及死皮一一去除{\r}
