Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}慢慢地排起了长队{\r}
