Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.52,0:16:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}起到缓解压力的作用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.48,0:16:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}中东地区极其炎热干燥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}大多数地表上都是寸草不生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}但是在红海里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.48,0:17:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}珊瑚礁的生长态势却十分旺盛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}近海水域的生物种类{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.56,0:17:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}几乎和热带雨林一样繁荣{\r}
