Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.12,0:17:26.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}只是为了休息和放松{\r}
