Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}昨天夜里都在近岸处进食{\r}
