Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}青少年海豚就开始探索环境{\r}
