Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.32,0:20:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}每个珊瑚礁都有明确的分界线{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}那就是它的城墙{\r}
