Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.40,0:20:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}这些壁垒能够保护城市不受海浪的侵袭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.20,0:20:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}不过这些城墙每日都要被涨潮覆盖两次{\r}
