Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.36,0:21:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}水手曾在故事里说过 有一只大海怪{\r}
