Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.84,0:22:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}在马尔代夫 潮水的规模达到最大时{\r}
