Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.00,0:22:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}蝠鲼的翼展宽达三米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.76,0:22:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}它们张着那狭槽似的大嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}从浮游生物旁边穿过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.84,0:23:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}蝠鲼生成了自己的旋涡{\r}
