Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}食物的供应被切断了{\r}
