Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.88,0:24:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}找到充足的空间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.20,0:24:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}从另一方面说{\r}
