Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.40,0:25:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnNoto Sans S Chinese Medium\fs20\bord1\shad2\4a&H64&\2c&H000000&\b0}因此这里在夜间{\r}
